  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine whether body fat distribution changes that occur with
      weight gain in women recovering from anorexia nervosa are transient or persistent, and if
      they are associated with other features of Metabolic Syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
